Program: Discovery
Title: Memory - part three
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jryz5
Last Broadcast Date: 10 June 2005
Exploring the science of memory. The programme explores what happens to memory in conditions like post traumatic stress disorder (PTSD) and depression and what it can teach us about the nature of our memory. Presenter: Pam Rutherford.